Title: Turn your ideas into songs with Suno on Microsoft Copilot
Description: We are excited to share that that we have partnered with Suno, a leader in artificial intelligence-based music creation to bring their capabilities to Microsoft Copilot. Through this partnership, people will have at their fingertips the ability, regardless of musical background, to create fun, clever, and personalized songs with a simple prompt.

Title: Wham! Authentication broker support lands in the Azure Identity libraries.
